# @sfcr/core-worker

- All solver calls go through `handleWorkerRequest` in `handler.ts`.
- Request/response types live in `protocol.ts` (`runBaseline`, `runScenario`, `validateModel`).
- Keep `worker.ts` a thin `onmessage` shim; no UI logic.
- Package `test` is compile-only (`tsc --noEmit`). Protocol tests live in `packages/web/test/workerHandler.test.ts`.
- Do not add React or DOM dependencies.
